content:
You can attach a few files for test decryption by packing them into an archive with zip, rar, tar, 7zip, 7z, tar.gz extensions of no more than 10 megabytes using the attach button directly in the chat.

If your archive weighs more than 10 megabytes, please use our file sharing service.
http://lockbitfss2w7co3ij6am6wox4xcurtgwukunx3yubcoe5cbxiqakxqd.onion
http://lockbitfsvf75glg226he5inkfgtuoakt4vgfhd7nfgghx5kwz5zo3ad.onion
http://lockbitfskq2fxclyfrop5yizyxpzu65w7pphsgthawcyb4gd27x62id.onion
For security reasons we do not click on other links you send in chat.
Please wait for a reply, sometimes it takes several hours due to possible time zone differences.
Hello?
Hello, you need pay
Did you take any of our data?
Please prove you can decrypt these
Hello
Did you take any data? Please generate a list of what was taken
Here is a part of file tree
and few samples of taken files
We assume you want some payment? Can we please have a full file tree so we can fully and fairly value your offering?
Full file tree is not a disclosed information until payment.
Then the amount we will be willing to pay you is significantly less
We can negotiate it still. It's in your interest to keep the information secure. Reputation is the most valuable thing in the world. Your CEO knows this best.
Seems we better message your customers whom data we took. I think they will able to pay.
it really would be easier to discuss payment if we knew everything you had
We have rules. Full file tree is disclosed information before payment. If you don't want to pay you'll see all the files in our blog.
We do not even know what you want yet
we want you pay 1,2m$
That is alot of money for us. We are meeting with the finance team to see what we can get
how is your meeting?
We cannot afford that much. Can you please work with us on price?
I don't see any offers from you
Leadership is in meetings regarding this. I will keep you updated.
Your time is up.
We just don't have that much. Would $100k do it?
Seems better we ask your clients for that money.
Please do not. We are trying. Can you come close to that?
i can give you 100k discount. Give me better offer
I'm still waiting
Ok let me work on it
Your time for respond i not unlimited. We are ready for publication
I understand but we cannot get that much together for this. Can you come down further?
I can give you discount but i didn't either see any real offers from you.
Offer or publication?

i need just 5 files 
how i cna get them
You don't care about data privacy?
how long do we have till you publish our data?
